name: Kelly Brook
description:
A TI of model and TV presenter Kelly Brook. I wasn't happy with the default in any SD model, so I made this.

Most of the training images are from her mid-20s (none were -18).

Of course, a large proportion were lingerie, so it does tend to produce lacy bras! None were NSFW though, so accidental nudity doesn't seem to be an issue.

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Run for another 4,500 steps, this seems a lot better. Gives good results in most photorealistic models.

Still likes to put her in lingerie / generate huge cleavage; the last lot of preview images got reported for TOS violation (despite no nudity), so I've deliberately had to choose ones that cover up her assets a bit. Sorry!
